data.description: This stunning property located in the vibrant and sought after 55+ community of Montevalle will not disappoint. The open design with vaulted ceilings and panorama windows in the main living space provide warm natural light and offers breathtaking views of the surrounding landscape and sunsets. Two of the four spacious bedrooms are peaceful en-suites with walk-in closets. The well designed layout includes features such as high-quality finishes, inside laundry, oversized 2-car garage, ample storage space, A/C unit and water softener. Scotts Valley is known for its mild micro-climate that sits just past the fog line. It boasts amenities such as parks, recreational facilities, shopping centers, restaurants, hiking trails, biking routes, local cinema, museums, art galleries, and cultural events regularly hosted in town. The Montevalle community includes a beautiful park, two pools, two ponds, picnic area in a redwood grove, putting green, clubhouse, and a lodge for your visitors to stay.
